{"tid":1993764,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林秀怡竟然被誤認係前AV女優水野朝陽：邊個咁大整蠱啊","createTime":"2020-04-29T04:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:26:41.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"741d39f2e009ecd3bceb9f0e72ec010cbb7fc3c8","tid":1993764,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"現年29歲的日本前AV女優水野朝陽於2013年2月出道至今，拍攝了多部作品，在AV界相當有人氣。她在2018年12月1日於個人Twitter上宣布，在出道6周年當日正式引退，傷了不少紛絲的心。不過她仍有經常更新自己的Twitter，update她的最新近況與粉絲同網民分享。呢日她就post了一張香港藝人林秀怡 (Kirby) 的相，究竟水野朝陽為何會特地post了Kirby的相呢？。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4400399/org/702cac62bb88f351b772cefa9c3cb787.jpg/TL_4FeXd3D1xE2NzDphbALAAH6TMpyb3OO4iBjjuIgY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4400399%2Forg%2F702cac62bb88f351b772cefa9c3cb787.jpg%2FTL_4FeXd3D1xE2NzDphbALAAH6TMpyb3OO4iBjjuIgY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2fe59593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年28歲的Kirby與水野朝陽可謂大纜都扯唔埋，不過她卻被人用她的相寫上了水野朝陽的資料，水野朝陽於是在她的Twitter post了那張相問大家是什麼一回事，看來她亦都充滿了疑惑。至於事件的另一女主角Kirby，亦有於她的IG上留言表示：「好對唔住水野朝陽，邊個咁大整蠱啊 #比女神見到個男人話似佢 #救命 #希望水野朝陽唔好介意 #仲要用張咁既相 #我無性感相啦咩 #好尷尬啊」有網民就留言話：「尋日睇佢twitter見到笑到抽筋。」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4400662/org/060882614bc7980ddbffbff3d4fa7e51.jpg/TZ5FhgxoVVX_QsGd5Sw_JHh-rrKnqmcGJuTfASbk3wE?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4400662%2Forg%2F060882614bc7980ddbffbff3d4fa7e51.jpg%2FTZ5FhgxoVVX_QsGd5Sw_JHh-rrKnqmcGJuTfASbk3wE%3Fv%3Dw640&h=00ccb9da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c5bdd7803d72b8d8480f038ebd74e3fed21d5a2","tid":1993764,"uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"不如佢退休你接力拍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badc6b51b6a663a5a4e40f6ed2b2d231e4b34a9b","tid":1993764,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"林秀怡都好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6026835e5b013ed3933330e130bc9909d97c8f0","tid":1993764,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"林秀怡好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁撚白滑大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d74921893caf2ed5921c8fb38cc88aead2cbe3a","tid":1993764,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔係容海恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a8fe35b1e83decaacf75d2cea8b6c865acc3a3","tid":1993764,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227711a4db93e61833344f25e379ae57877c0083","tid":1993764,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d74921893caf2ed5921c8fb38cc88aead2cbe3a","tid":1993764,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔係容海恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"容海恩後生果陣=水野"},{"pid":"90b3b1f6fc02534eea8e5cef77f4c9471a027cd7","tid":1993764,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:26: